summary: This document is a series of bank statements (TD Simple Checking) for an account from December 2018 through August 2019. It shows detailed daily transaction activity including deposits (primarily federal salary payments and tax refunds), debit card purchases, electronic payments, and transfers. The statements are part of the Epstein case document release, suggesting this account may be relevant to the investigation, possibly belonging to a person of interest or victim. This document is a bank account history inquiry for a TD Simple Checking account, showing debit and credit card transactions from August 12-19, 2019. The transactions are primarily retail purchases in beach towns in Delaware and Maryland, with no direct mention of Epstein-related individuals or events.
